rComments: She is so amazing and helped to inspire me to work harder. She is one of a kind.

She's an airhead.  Very difficult to follow because she is scatter brained. She's all over the place and no one knows what she is doing least of all her.  Poor teaching methods. She is not very helpful.  She needs to improve how she articulates her thoughts and ideas to the class.
Really knows her stuff, her enthusiasm makes you want to do well and take part in class discussions.

Nice person, not great prof. Student presentations take over class (lazy prof.?). workload very taxing. Word count on assignments seem to count for more than quality. a potentially excellent course, but a missed opportunity in this case.
